img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4924c677f6ef64e91b3d53526239c6f014da2a9","tid":2304973,"uid":203226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"著短袖咁渣 我今日唔撚著"},{"pid":"3b653ee23f14588544ff0b706015f2ce245c8558","tid":2304973,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"冇咩黑絲睇"},{"pid":"3f4db02b7f12f939ab2920aa2b24390f2a12beee","tid":2304973,"uid":192024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；西伯利亞人作日光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n連登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』"},{"pid":"8f37a4b4a782c12136a483002050a659c169de79","tid":2304973,"uid":162037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:49:22.000Z","msg":"好凍阿，唔似18-22度，我覺得好似8-12度咁凍既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能我虧"},{"pid":"ab2d1522493fd0e444d523e4e0cdc104d6298659","tid":2304973,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T10:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d225cc54f4ffeecc45cfb77a93981aefb7cd1ba9","tid":2304973,"uid":248695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T10:11:28.000Z","msg":"出返幾次火先啦蓋清"},{"pid":"d12cabfdd34c401f760039f17275287e306a1323","tid":2304973,"uid":266635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"又舊po循環再用，使唔使咁環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b60311e4a16b2031500ebac5506305138f921f9","tid":2304973,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse